   Chapman, Mark A.; Nambeesan, Savithri; Shaffer, Hunter; Burke, John M., Univ Georgia, Dept Plant Pathol, Athens, GA 30602 USA.
   Tang, Shunxue; Draeger, Doerthe; Barb, Jessica G.; Knapp, Steven J., Univ Georgia, Inst Plant Breeding Genet \& Genom, Athens, GA 30602 USA.},
