   Ferrer, Miriam M., Univ Autonoma Yucatan, Dept Ecol, Merida 97000, Yucatan, Mexico.
   Good-Avila, Sara V., Univ Winnipeg, Dept Biol, Winnipeg, MB R3B 2E9, Canada.
